    21	    It is the unit of work the CLI and Provider hand to each other:
    22	
    23	    * :meth:`ordered` returns creates/updates in dependency order,
    24	      followed by deletes in reverse dependency order.
    25	    * :meth:`is_clean` is the "no actionable changes" predicate used to
    26	      drive the ``plan`` / ``diff`` exit code (2 when non-clean).
    27	    * The ``creates`` / ``updates`` / ``deletes`` / ``conflicts`` /
