    86	    applies to ``changes`` / ``order`` afterwards — important because
    87	    downstream code (renderers, providers) inspects the Plan across
    88	    multiple call sites.
    89	    """
    90	    return Plan(manifest_name=manifest_name, changes=list(changes), order=list(order))

